  "prompt": "What are some good IVF and Fertility clinics in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "There are several reputable IVF and fertility clinics in Hyderabad. Here are some that are well-regarded:\n\n1. **Dr. Padmaja Fertility Center**\n   - Known for offering personalized care and advanced fertility treatments including IVF, IUI, and surrogacy.\n\n2. **Oasis Fertility**\n   - Offers a wide range of infertility treatments and has a team of experienced doctors. They focus on patient-centric care and have good success rates.\n\n3. **Hegde Fertility**\n   - Provides comprehensive fertility treatments such as IVF, ICSI, IUI, and fertility preservation. They have a strong emphasis on research and technology.\n\n4. **Fakih IVF**\n   - Offers various fertility treatments and diagnostics. Known for its expert team and advanced medical facilities.\n\n5. **Nova IVF Fertility**\n   - Part of a large network with multiple centers in India, known for its high success rates and experienced medical staff.\n\n6. **Sree Fertility & IVF Center**\n   - Offers a full range of infertility treatments and diagnostic services. The clinic is known for its personalized approach to treatment.\n\n7. **Southern Gem Hospital**\n   - Provides comprehensive fertility services, from basic to advanced treatments. The hospital has a team of skilled professionals and modern facilities.\n\nWhen choosing a fertility clinic, consider factors such as the clinic's success rates, the qualifications and experience of the medical staff, the facilities available, and patient reviews. It is also important to feel comfortable with the clinic and its approach to treatment.",
